{
  "text": "Reacting FAFS in an anhydrous CH 3 CN/NaN 3 slurry at r.t. for 3 h the following main product shown in Scheme 11 has been identified by 19 F-NMR. The nucleophilic A/E sum of H 2 O 2 to FAFS was studied both in an aqueous biphasic system [CITATION_1] as well as in an anhydrous system. Scheme 12 shows the reactions involved in the peroxidation reaction. Scheme 12. Diallylperoxide reaction mechanism.",
